race.comment: RATTLE AND HUM (3) has been right there in all three runs this preparation and looks to be working up to another victory. Has placed around this circuit, gets 2kg off with the claim and draws the inside alley. Ticks a few boxes for a race like this. TAJAWAL (5) was well in the betting at Ipswich last time out and didn't let backers down with a dominant win. Maloney sticks in the irons and should be going very close again. SUN WORSHIPPER (1) is another to get some weight off and will be rock-hard fit for this. Sure to be hitting the line with gusto. FARWEST (8) should be ready to peak now fourth run back and looks a must for the multiples. SIR LAMORAK (6) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be slept on.
